08/09/2003
SKOPJE, Macedonia -- Macedonian police reported that they have seized a shipment of 54 kg of heroin, worth 500,000 euros. 
The drugs were found in a truck travelling from Skopje in the direction of Kumanovo. 
Authorities believe the heroin was being smuggled to Serbia-Montenegro. 
(AP, AFP, Reuters - 07/09/03)
